These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, ship, roller, trike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the person driving the roller is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the person driving the roller##6
5. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Transport   | trike  | bike | roller | ship  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

