.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, balloon-flower, marigold, begonia
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, journalist, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the project-manager##8
2. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
3. the person who growsdaffodil is the journalist##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere between the person who growsmarigold and the designer##7
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
7. the designer is not to the left of the designer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Flower   | marigold | balloon-flower          | begonia | daffodil     |
| Job    | nurse      | project-manager | designer | journalist |

