.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, nurse, paramedic
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, almond-milk, soy-milk
1. the person drinking water is not to the left of the nurse##8
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the electrician is in an even position##4
5. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
6. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
7. the paramedic is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | bartender | electrician | nurse     | paramedic |
| Beverage   | mirinda    | soy-milk   | water | almond-milk    |

