.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, russian, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the indian##1
4. the pakistani is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
5. the australian is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the australian is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the russian is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | russian   | indian         | pakistani   | australian    |
| Sport         | parkour | weightlifting | soccer | lacrosse |

