.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
City: venice, berlin, london, colone
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, handball, rugby
1. the person traveling to colone is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to berlin##7
2. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the person traveling to colone is somewhere between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to venice##7
4. the person traveling to london is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person traveling to berlin and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to colone##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person traveling to venice##8
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| City   | berlin   | london | colone | venice    |
| Sport         | climbing | rugby   | handball   | cycling |

