2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
3. the spanish is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the american##5
6. the french is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
7. the french is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality          | french | dutch | american  | spanish |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | pop         | indie | ambient |

