4. the person traveling to colone is not to the left of the person traveling to venice##8
5. the person traveling to colone is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
