2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
3. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person eating tomato##7
5. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person eating apricot##8
6. the person eating apricot is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person eating plum##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
