4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, whist, scrabble
1. the writer is between the person playing billiard and the person playing whist##2
2. the person playing mah-jongg is not the librarian##6
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the chef##1
4. the manager is not to the right of the chef##8
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the chef##3
6. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Job         | manager | chef      | writer   | librarian  |
| Game   | scrabble    | billiard | mah-jongg | whist |

