2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
3. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
5. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Birthday   | october     | june | april | september |
| Transport     | quad-bike | scooter  | car    | boat   |

