3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the brazilian##1
4. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
5. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the brazilian##7
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
8. the argentine is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | argentine | brazilian         | indian    | mexican       |
| Sport      | handball | skateboarding | biathlon | ice-hockey |

