3. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking tea and the person who growszinnia##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
6. the person who growsorchid is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growsiris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | 7up     | almond-milk | tea        | sprite       |
