2. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8
3. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
4. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
7. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3     |    4    |
| Birthday    | may   | july    | june   | october |
| Hobby   | cooking | photography | skydiving | dancing |

