The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, jet-ski, trike
1. the gothic-revival house is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
2. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the farmhouse house##8
3. the colonial house is somewhere between the farmhouse house and the gothic-revival house##7
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
5. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
6. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
7. the colonial house is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| House         | cape-cod  | gothic-revival | colonial  | farmhouse  |
| Transport   | bike | car   | trike | jet-ski |

