.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball, surfing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is swimming##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Sport   | volleyball | skateboarding      | surfing     | swimming     |

 